 Chatbot c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng tr\u00ean nhi\u1ec1u n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng kh\u00e1c nhau nh\u01b0 website, fanpage Facebook, \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng nh\u1eafn tin, gi\u00fap t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng h\u00f3a vi\u1ec7c tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi, h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng, v\u00e0 t\u0103ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Trong th\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n nhanh ch\u00f3ng, chatbot \u0111ang tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee5 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu gi\u00fap doanh nghi\u1ec7p ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m th\u1eddi gian, n\u00e2ng cao ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 v\u00e0 t\u1ed1i \u01b0u h\u00f3a quy tr\u00ecnh b\u00e1n h\u00e0ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/supership.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/Chatbot.png\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-7078 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/supership.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/Chatbot.png\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" width=\"1187\" height=\"742\" srcset=\"https:\/\/supership.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/Chatbot.png 800w, https:\/\/supership.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/Chatbot-300x188.png 300w, https:\/\/supership.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/Chatbot-768x480.png 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1187px) 100vw, 1187px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<h2><b>2. L\u1ee3i \u00edch c\u1ee7a ChatBot trong kinh doanh<\/b><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng chatbot mang l\u1ea1i r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ee3i \u00edch trong ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng kinh doanh, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 trong vi\u1ec7c ch\u0103m s\u00f3c kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng v\u00e0 marketing:<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&#8211; Ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m chi ph\u00ed nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">: Chatbot c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n vi\u00ean, gi\u1ea3m thi\u1ec3u chi ph\u00ed thu\u00ea nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&#8211; Ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng 24\/7<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">: Kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n b\u1edfi th\u1eddi gian l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c, chatbot lu\u00f4n s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 l\u00fac n\u00e0o.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&#8211; T\u0103ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c v\u00e0 tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">: Chatbot gi\u00fap tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi nhanh c\u00e1c c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi, t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 t\u0103ng s\u1ef1 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u00e0 gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&#8211; Thu th\u1eadp d\u1eef li\u1ec7u kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">: Chatbot ghi nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin, s\u1edf th\u00edch, h\u00e0nh vi ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng gi\u00fap doanh nghi\u1ec7p ph\u00e2n t\u00edch v\u00e0 c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n h\u00f3a chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e1n h\u00e0ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&#8211; T\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng h\u00f3a quy tr\u00ecnh b\u00e1n h\u00e0ng<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">: T\u1eeb gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m, t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ebfn x\u1eed l\u00fd \u0111\u01a1n h\u00e0ng, chatbot gi\u00fap t\u1ed1i \u01b0u h\u00f3a c\u00e1c b\u01b0\u1edbc mua s\u1eafm online.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng l\u1ee3i \u00edch n\u00e0y, chatbot tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee5 quan tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng cao n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c c\u1ea1nh tranh c\u1ee7a doanh nghi\u1ec7p.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/khachhang.supership.vn\/register?referral=S919808\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-6662\" src=\"https:\/\/supership.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/SuperShip-300x100.png\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"X\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng Affiliate hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 cho kinh doanh online\" width=\"1200\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"https:\/\/supership.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/SuperShip-300x100.png 300w, https:\/\/supership.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/SuperShip-1024x341.png 1024w, https:\/\/supership.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/SuperShip-768x256.png 768w, https:\/\/supership.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/SuperShip.png 1200w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h2><b>3. C\u00e1ch t\u1ea1o Chatbot cho website<\/b><\/h2>\n<h3><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><b>3.1 Chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u00e1c y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft<\/b><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi t\u1ea1o chatbot cho website, b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u00e1c y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n sau:<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&#8211; X\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau: B\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n chatbot h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 g\u00ec? Tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi FAQ, t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m hay h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt?<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&#8211; K\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n h\u1ed9i tho\u1ea1i: L\u00ean k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n c\u00e1c t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng, c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi th\u01b0\u1eddng g\u1eb7p v\u00e0 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1ee9ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&#8211; N\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng chatbot: L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn c\u00f4ng c\u1ee5 ho\u1eb7c n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng chatbot, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 c\u00e1c ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed ho\u1eb7c tr\u1ea3 ph\u00ed.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&#8211; Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf giao di\u1ec7n chat: \u0110\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o chatbot c\u00f3 giao di\u1ec7n th\u00e2n thi\u1ec7n, d\u1ec5 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng tr\u00ean website.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><strong><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">3.2 C\u00e1c b\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1ea1o chatbot cho website<\/span><\/strong><\/h3>\n<p><b>B\u01b0\u1edbc 1: <\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ch\u1ecdn n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng t\u1ea1o chatbot: C\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ea1o chatbot cho website nh\u01b0 ManyChat, Tawk.to, Chatfuel hay n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng chatbot t\u00edch h\u1ee3p s\u1eb5n trong h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng qu\u1ea3n tr\u1ecb website.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>B\u01b0\u1edbc 2: <\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">T\u1ea1o t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n v\u00e0 k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i website: \u0110\u0103ng k\u00fd t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n tr\u00ean n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn, sau \u0111\u00f3 k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i chatbot v\u1edbi website th\u00f4ng qua \u0111o\u1ea1n m\u00e3 nh\u00fang (code script).<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>B\u01b0\u1edbc 3: <\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Thi\u1ebft l\u1eadp k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n v\u00e0 lu\u1ed3ng h\u1ed9i tho\u1ea1i: L\u1eadp k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n chi ti\u1ebft cho chatbot theo c\u00e1c t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng th\u01b0\u1eddng g\u1eb7p. S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng, nh\u1eadn d\u1ea1ng t\u1eeb kh\u00f3a v\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>B\u01b0\u1edbc 4: <\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">T\u00f9y ch\u1ec9nh giao di\u1ec7n chatbot: Thay \u0111\u1ed5i m\u00e0u s\u1eafc, h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n chatbot \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c th\u00e2n thi\u1ec7n v\u1edbi kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>B\u01b0\u1edbc 5: <\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ki\u1ec3m tra v\u00e0 ch\u1ea1y th\u1eed chatbot: Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng, b\u1ea1n n\u00ean ki\u1ec3m tra k\u1ef9 c\u00e1c t\u00ednh n\u0103ng, s\u1eeda l\u1ed7i v\u00e0 t\u1ed1i \u01b0u tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>B\u01b0\u1edbc 5: <\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Tri\u1ec3n khai tr\u00ean website v\u00e0 theo d\u00f5i hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3: \u0110\u1eb7t chatbot l\u00ean website v\u00e0 theo d\u00f5i c\u00e1c ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c, ph\u1ea3n h\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h2><b>4. C\u00e1ch t\u1ea1o Chatbot cho Fanpage<\/b><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Fanpage Facebook l\u00e0 k\u00eanh b\u00e1n h\u00e0ng tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn. T\u1ea1o chatbot cho Fanpage gi\u00fap t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi tin nh\u1eafn kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng, gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1p th\u1eafc m\u1eafc nhanh ch\u00f3ng, thu th\u1eadp th\u00f4ng tin v\u00e0 t\u0103ng t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111\u01a1n h\u00e0ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>C\u00e1c b\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1ea1o chatbot cho Fanpage:<\/b><\/p>\n<p><b>B\u01b0\u1edbc 1: <\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ch\u1ecdn n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng t\u1ea1o chatbot: N\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn l\u00e0 ManyChat, Chatfuel, Ahachat&#8230; C\u00e1c n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng n\u00e0y h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u00edch h\u1ee3p tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi Fanpage Facebook.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>B\u01b0\u1edbc 2: <\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">K\u1ebft n\u1ed1i Fanpage v\u1edbi n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng chatbot: \u0110\u0103ng nh\u1eadp v\u00e0o n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng, c\u1ea5p quy\u1ec1n truy c\u1eadp Fanpage v\u00e0 k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ec3 chatbot c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng tr\u00ean trang.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>B\u01b0\u1edbc 3: <\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">T\u1ea1o k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n tr\u00f2 chuy\u1ec7n: X\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng c\u00e1c c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi th\u01b0\u1eddng g\u1eb7p, k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m, x\u1eed l\u00fd \u0111\u01a1n h\u00e0ng t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>B\u01b0\u1edbc 4: <\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">C\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb7t c\u00e1c t\u00ednh n\u0103ng n\u00e2ng cao: T\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng g\u1eedi tin nh\u1eafn ch\u00e0o m\u1eebng, g\u1eedi tin nh\u1eafn theo l\u1ecbch, g\u1ee3i \u00fd s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean h\u00e0nh vi kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>B\u01b0\u1edbc 5: <\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ki\u1ec3m tra v\u00e0 k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t chatbot: Th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m chatbot v\u1edbi c\u00e1c t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng kh\u00e1c nhau, s\u1eeda l\u1ed7i v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ch\u1ea1y tr\u00ean Fanpage.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>B\u01b0\u1edbc 6: <\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Theo d\u00f5i v\u00e0 t\u1ed1i \u01b0u chatbot: S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng b\u00e1o c\u00e1o c\u1ee7a n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng chatbot \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111o l\u01b0\u1eddng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3, c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n c\u00e1c k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n nh\u1eb1m n\u00e2ng cao tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/khachhang.supership.vn\/register?referral=S919808\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-6663\" src=\"https:\/\/supership.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/SuperAI--300x100.png\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"Ti\u1ebfp th\u1ecb li\u00ean k\u1ebft TikTok l\u00e0 g\u00ec? SuperAI\" width=\"1266\" height=\"422\" srcset=\"https:\/\/supership.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/SuperAI--300x100.png 300w, https:\/\/supership.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/SuperAI--1024x341.png 1024w, https:\/\/supership.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/SuperAI--768x256.png 768w, https:\/\/supership.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/SuperAI-.png 1200w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1266px) 100vw, 1266px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h2><b>5. M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p chatbot AI<\/b><\/h2>\n<h3><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><b>5.1 Harafunnel<\/b><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Harafunnel l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng chatbot AI n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam, cung c\u1ea5p c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng